result.name: Lei Garden Restaurant Central

reviews.text: I love the seating here you get a good amount of privacy. The food is always good , lei garden standard. You must go here for the Peking duck

worst lei garden experience among all branches. their famous charsiu sold out during lunch time (probably kept for VIPs), soup rice with almost no rice, and wrong bill. the stars are for the only impressive dish (fish soup noodles) and great service.
Very authentic Cantonese food and excellent execution. Love the BBQ pork (melt in the mouth), assorted dim sum and Cantonese soup. It has become my new favorite Cantonese restaurant in HK.

Very crowded during the weekend lunch time (yumcha) and not so good service with not so special cantonese dishes...
But still quite good location with the Express train to the HK airport if you are a tourist and still you can try the various cantonese dishes. But If I were you, I will choose other option.

This branch of famous Lei Garden inside the luxurious IFC mall does not live up to expectation. The interior is posh and luxurious. The food quality was not constant, sometimes it was good sometimes disappointing. But most of all the service could be very bad during the busy hours. I'd better eat somewhere else rather than stick to a big name! How sad.

result.formatted_address: 香港中環港景街1號國際金融中心一期
result.name: 利苑酒家 中環

reviews.text:
일요일 저녁 8시쯤 예약없이 방문
운이 좋게도? 자리도 있고 베이징덕을 먹을수 있었음

국민메뉴 베이징 덕과 크리스피 포크를 주문했는데
워낙 유명한 음식점이라 그런지 맛은 그저 그랬고
제 기준 이 조합의 주문은 너무 느끼해 식후 탄산 원샷

굳이 웨이팅을 하며 먹어야 할 필요가 있을까 함

출국전 인터넷으로 예약을 하고 간 곳.
딤섬도 좋았지만 크리스피포크의 맛이 인상적이었습니다. 마지막으로 나온 볶음밥 또한 일품이었습니다. 
미슐랭 별 하나의 가치는 충분한 곳입니다.

재작년에 가보고 기억이 좋아서 또 갔습니당
둘이 갔기때문에 음식을 두개시켰는데 
넘나 고기만 시켰는지 나중에 느끼해서 
오리조림(?)은 몇조각만 먹었네여
깔끔해서 괜찮은데
느끼할수있으니 야채랑 같이 시키시는고 추천드립니당
저 큐브 바베큐는 맛있는데 상당히 작아요 
손바닥정도?ㅋㅋ
곁들여 나오는 겨자 소스를 베이징덕에 같이 먹으니 맛있더라고요
服務及食物質素上佳，以中環餐館來說，價錢是可接受水平
I love the seating here you get a good amount of privacy. The food is always good , lei garden standard. You must go here for the Peking duck
